{"tid":1497943,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"CEF 持續進修基金 (PolyU HKCC新生可留意)","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:48:27.000Z","uid":201545,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"daf32e52a0bf3caaf67d3ddb935cf0d972bc87c0","tid":1497943,"uid":201545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:55:28.000Z","msg":"各位新課程新生<br />\n<br />\nCEF 持續進修基金<br />\n需於開學前(2Sep前)寄到辦事處開立戶口<br />\n<br />\n可到<a href=\"https://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/cef/tc/preparation/course_search.php查詢合資格課程\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wfsfaa.gov.hk%2Fcef%2Ftc%2Fpreparation%2Fcourse_search.php%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E5%90%88%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E8%AA%B2%E7%A8%8B&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1UpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=1bd813ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/cef/tc/preparation/course_search.php查詢合資格課程</a><br />\n<br />\nPolyU HKCC Associate Degree in Business programmes<br />\n<br />\n申請表要向General Office (WK 2/F)蓋印並寄出<br />\nbusiness 科同學<br />\nSem 1修讀CCN2003 Introduction to Marketing or<br />\nCCN2101 Financial Accounting可開立戶口<br />\n成績合格便可申請80%學費退還<br />\n<br />\n詳情可向General Office or 37460123查詢<br />\n<br />\n申請表可向民政事務處索取或上網下載<br />\n<br />\n欲申請把握開學前時間辦理"},{"pid":"9210aa1cfb3f5c854b15f67c8e6fe9ed32319f60","tid":1497943,"uid":306575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"ching你條link用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ed1e5ae15c5d1f6ecfb644f1dd0d3f85d1a3c0","tid":1497943,"uid":201545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9210aa1cfb3f5c854b15f67c8e6fe9ed32319f60","tid":1497943,"uid":306575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"ching你條link用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wfsfaa.gov.hk/cef/en/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg